@ParametersAreNonnullByDefault

Package de.dennis_kempf.squidward

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Automaton
    Automaton with a finite set of States and Transitions.
    State
    State of an Automaton.
    State.Action
    Action that will be executed upon state entry or exit.
    Transition<T>
    Transition from one State of an Automaton to another.
    Transition.Action<T>
    Action which will be executed if an transaction is taken.
    Transition.Guard<T>
    Guard which has to be satisfied for an transition to be taken.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ImmutableAutomaton
    Implementation of Automaton whose sets of states and transitions are immutable.
    ImmutableAutomaton.Builder
    Builder for construction of an ImmutableAutomaton.
    ImmutableState
    Immutable implementation of State.
    ImmutableState.Builder
    Builder for construction of an ImmutableState.
    ImmutableTransition<T>
    Immutable implementation of Transition.
    ImmutableTransition.Builder<T>
    Builder for construction of an ImmutableTransition.
